  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Made from the horns of a great buffalo, this Orcish-Hornbow is a massive compound bow that requires a +4 strength bonus to use.</p><p>It also requires custom ammunition, as regular arrows are snapped into pieces by the greater forces exerted by this weapon. Properly built and treated arrows for GBH are enchanted at least +1 to survive being fired out of it. On impact, they explode in a small but potent 2' diameter orange fireball.</p><p>The noise of the impacts from this weapon can be heard for miles. It is easily as loud as most firearms.</p><img src=\"Art%20-%20Characters/halforc_female_archer_great_hornbow_orcish.webp\" />",
      "instructions": "",
      "unidentified": ""
    },
